requests:


CRUD  view -> create,retrive,update,delete

GET -> retrive data / list data

POST -> update,delete,change data



how to send retrieve data on a request:

use HttpResponse(variable.render(context))
with a variable = get_template("file name") and context={a dictionary}

or 

render(request,filename,context)



to learn more about forms,models ,modelform

